translations: n．废话，胡言乱语：指无意义或难以理解的话。
· He was talking a lot of mumbo jumbo.

phrs.translation: 天书, 繁文缛节, 神秘的力量, 难懂的术语
全心感受, 爱, 莫名其妙的话, 胡言乱语

sentences.sentence: It's all full of psychoanalytic mumbo-jumbo.
sentences.translation: 这里面全是精神分析的一派胡言。

sentences.sentence: It was descendants of those Europeans who came up with this apocalypse mumbo-jumbo.
sentences.translation: 正是这些欧洲人的后代想出了这种胡编乱造的末日预言。

sentences.sentence: Eventually, Mumbo and his friends decided to ask the child.
sentences.translation: 最终，马姆博和他的朋友决定问这个孩子。
